data.description: Welcome to Indian Springs Country Club in Boynton Beach is 55+ Community with NO Mandatory Membership and low HOA fees. 2 bedroom/2 bathroom home with a two-car garage. As you walk in, you are welcomed by a spacious open floor plan perfect for entertainment and dining! Beautiful custom kitchen cabinets and all brand new appliances. The stove has a convection oven and an air fryer and the appliances work with the LG app. Recline in your patio with windows that are removable and a gorgeous Golf Course &  waterfront view. Both bathrooms have been beautifully re-done with brand new cabinets and flooring. Unwind in the beautiful Roman tub in your master bathroom. Take a look at this lovely home today! **A/C is 3 years old**
